// Basic theme:
// This part exists from "1" to "6".
// "1" to "5" is everything red in the standard theme (this does not include buttons which have destructive functions (like "Clear")).
// 6 is the text inside of the red boxes in the standard theme, it is recommended to only change this if it is hard to read. 
// First get the rgb values of the color you want to make the basic theme and divide all 3 values (red, blue and green) by 255.
