// Change "Yb" to the value you got for dividing the "blue" value by 255.
// Change "Zg" to the value you got for dividing the "green" value by 255.
// Leave the "alpha" value as is.
// You will need to do this 10 times in total (from "1" to "5", both for lightColor and darkColor).

